    "body": "Reverts NVIDIA/TensorRT-LLM#12738 due to a test-time/semantic conflict with https://github.com/NVIDIA/TensorRT-LLM/pull/13631.\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **Bug Fixes & Changes**\n  * Removed support for unquantized BF16 Mixture of Experts (MoE) execution paths.\n  * Simplified MoE backend selection logic.\n\n* **Tests**\n  * Updated test configurations and simplified test parameters for MoE backend variants.\n  * Added test waivers for specific configurations.\n\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
